Program: Outlook
Title: Cancer Treatment in India
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr73
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Cancer in India, a look at treatment and support networks available to sufferers there. Also, an inteview with Diane Warren - the Oscar-nominated unknown songwriter responsible for hits by Cher and Celine Dion. Sporting diets - rower Louis Attrill and Kate Allenby talk about what they eat and how it helps them win. Presenter: Heather Payton. Show less